Makana Town Planning official Gemma Meaton has been nominated by the South African Planning Institute (SAPI) for its National Planning Awards. Photo: Sue Maclennan Makana Town Planning Official Gemma Meaton has been nominated by the South African Planning Institute (SAPI) for its National Planning Awards. The award recognises special efforts, outstanding contributions and extraordinary performance in all aspects of the planning profession, in both the government and private sectors.